title: This Week - S13E15 - 2015.01.15 - 468p x264
description:
POLITICAL: This Week
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Thursday 15th January 2015 
Time: 23:35 to 00:20 

Andrew Neil looks at the arguments over printing cartoons of the Prophet Muhammad with comic Shazia Mirza and journalist Nabila Ramdani, who are both Muslim but hold opposing views about the issue. There is a review of the political week with a film from Adam Boulton of Sky News, before the issues are debated by Michael Portillo, Diane Abbott and Miranda Green. And F1 presenter Suzi Perry is also be on the sofa. Crack open the Blue Nun and prepare to watch public service broadcasting at its best.
